Summary: 10 orange like spots in the sky that looked like had flames
divs: Sighting DetailsThere was a group of us outside..My son saw to orange spots in the sky and called my husband...They witnessed the organge objects, then called me and some other over...I then saw in a straight line of them coming and the other orange like objects caught up with the others...then they disappaered...We all agreeded that they were not planes nor helicopters..but something we had never seen before..It was really strange...We have video and can submit it when my husband downloads it...Thank you
